Rules.InvariantScript: If(IsBlank(ThisItem.Tooltip), ThisItem.Text, ThisItem.Tooltip) & If(ThisItem.Disabled, Char(10) & "Disabled: " & ThisItem.DisabledTooltip)

"
Developed by Apache iX Ltd
App Version: " & Sidebar_v1__.AppRelease.Release & "." & Sidebar_v1__.AppRelease.Fix & " (" & Sidebar_v1__.AppRelease.Type & ")
"
"Click to get more info about Apache iX and this app's release notes"

"data:image/svg+xml," & EncodeUrl(
    "<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' standalone='no'?>
<!DOCTYPE svg PUBLIC '-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN' 'http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd'>
<svg version='1.1'
    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
    xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink' preserveAspectRatio='xMidYMid meet' viewBox='0 0 " & Parent.Width & " " & Parent.Height & "' width='" & Parent.Width & "' height='" & Parent.Height & "'>
    <g>
        <g>
            <filter id='shadow' x='-20%' y='-20%' width='200%' height='200%' filterUnits='userSpaceOnUse' primitiveUnits='userSpaceOnUse'>
                <feFlood></feFlood>
                <feComposite in2='SourceAlpha' operator='in'></feComposite>
                <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur & "'></feGaussianBlur>
                <feOffset dx='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX & "' dy='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY & "' result='afterOffset'></feOffset>
                <feFlood flood-color='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Color & "' flood-opacity='" & Substitute(Text(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Opacity), ",", ".") & "'></feFlood>
                <feComposite in2='afterOffset' operator='in'></feComposite>
                <feMorphology operator='dilate' radius='1'></feMorphology>
                <feComposite in2='SourceAlpha' operator='out'></feComposite>
            </filter>
        </g>        
        <rect 
            id='boxForFill' 
            x='" & Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) & "' 
            y='" & Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY,0) & "' 
            width='" & Parent.Width - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 + Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) & "' 
            height='" & Parent.Height - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY,0) - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 + Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY, 0) & "' 
            fill='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.Fill & "' 
            stroke='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.BorderColor & "' stroke-width='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.BorderThickness & "'
            fill-opacity='" & Substitute(Text(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.Opacity), ",", ".") & "'
            rx='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.Radius & "'
        />
        <rect 
            id='boxForShadow' 
            x='" & Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) & "' 
            y='" & Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY,0) & "' 
            width='" & Parent.Width - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 + Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetX, 0) & "' 
            height='" & Parent.Height - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 - Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY,0) - Max(Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.Blur * 3 + Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogShadow.OffsetY, 0) & "' 
            rx='" & Sidebar_v1__.Style.DialogBox.Radius & "'
            filter='url(#shadow)'/>
    </g>
</svg>"
)

"Enter a detailed description." 
& Char(10) & Char(10) & 
Switch(rad_Type.Selected.Value,
    "Bug", "Ensure there is enough information for developer to reproduce the bug.",
    "Request", "Explain how beneficial/important the feature would be; this will help prioritisation."
)
If(IsBlank(txt_Title.Text), "Add a descriptive title for your feedback.", "")

    Width: {
        Collapsed: 50,
        Expanded: 300
    },        
    Fill: Color.DarkGray,
    MenuItem: {
        Color: Color.White, 
        HoverFill: Color.Gray,
        FontSize: 14,
        IconSize: 50,
        IconPadding: 10
    },
    Separator: {
        VerticalPadding: 5,
        Thickness: 2,
        Color: Color.Gray
    },

    // The following standard components are used in the Submit Feedback dialog; this should be replaced by the app specific definition.

        // Standard app colours...

        AppColor:       ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
        AppColorShade:  ColorValue("#ffd699FF"),
        Action:         ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),

            RadiusTopLeft: 10, RadiusTopright: 10, RadiusBottomLeft: 10, RadiusBottomRight: 10
        },
        Secondary: {
            Color: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            Fill: Color.White,
            BorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            BorderStyle: Solid, BorderThickness: 1, 

            HoverColor: Color.White,
            HoverFill: ColorFade(ColorValue("#0275d8FF"), -20%),
            HoverBorderColor: ColorFade(ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),-20%),

            FocusedBorderThickness: 2, 
            FocusedBorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),

            PressedFill: ColorFade(ColorValue("#0275d8FF"), -20%),

            RadiusTopLeft: 10, RadiusTopright: 10, RadiusBottomLeft: 10, RadiusBottomRight: 10
        }
    },

    Labels: {
        H1: {
            // Not really used in headings.
            Overflow: Overflow.Hidden, Wrap: true,
            DisabledColor: RGBA(166, 166, 166, 1), PressedColor: Color.Black, HoverColor: Color.Black,
            BorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), PressedBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), HoverBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), DisabledBorderColor: RGBA(56, 56, 56, 1), FocusedBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1),

            // Main properties for labels.
            Color: ColorValue("#303030FF"),
            Font: Font.'Open Sans',
            FontWeight: FontWeight.Bold,      
            Size: 18,
            Italic: false, Underline: false, Strikethrough: false,
            Align: Align.Left, VerticalAlign: VerticalAlign.Middle
        },
        PrimaryText: {
            // Main properties for labels.
            Color: ColorValue("#303030FF"),
            Font: Font.'Open Sans',
            FontWeight: FontWeight.Normal,      
            Size: 10,
            Italic: false, Underline: false, Strikethrough: false,
            Align: Align.Left, VerticalAlign: VerticalAlign.Middle,
            
            // Not really used in headings.

            DisabledColor: RGBA(166, 166, 166, 1), PressedColor: Color.Black, HoverColor: Color.Black,
            BorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), PressedBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), HoverBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1), DisabledBorderColor: RGBA(56, 56, 56, 1), FocusedBorderColor: RGBA(0, 18, 107, 1),
            BorderStyle: Solid, BorderThickness: 0, FocusedBorderThickness: 0,
            Fill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0), DisabledFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0), PressedFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0), HoverFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0),
            LineHeight: 1.2,
            PaddingTop: 5, PaddingRight: 5, PaddingBottom: 5, PaddingLeft: 5
        }
    },    

    Controls: {
        Textbox: {
            BorderStyle: BorderStyle.Solid,
            BorderThickness: 1,
            BorderColor: ColorValue("#D3D3D3FF"),
            FocusedBorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            FocusedBorderThickness: 2,
            HoverBorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            PressedBorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            BorderRadius: 0,

            Font: Font.'Open Sans',
            Size: 10,
            Color: ColorValue("#303030FF"),
            FontWeight: FontWeight.Normal,
            Italic: false, Underline: false, Strikethrough: false,

            PaddingTop: 5, PaddingRight: 5, PaddingBottom: 5, PaddingLeft: 12,

            Fill: Color.White,
            HoverFill: ColorValue("#8dc1ed66"),
            PressedFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0),

            HoverColor: Color.Black,
            PressedColor: Color.White,

            Clear: false,
            LineHeight: 1.2,
            Align: Align.Left,
            
            DisabledColor: RGBA(166, 166, 166, 1),
            DisabledFill: RGBA(244, 244, 244, 1),
            DisabledBorderColor: RGBA(166, 166, 166, 1)
        },
        Radio: {
            BorderStyle: None,
            BorderThickness: 0,
            BorderColor: Color.Black,
            FocusedBorderColor: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            FocusedBorderThickness: 2,
            
            Font: Font.'Open Sans',
            Size: 10,
            Color: ColorValue("#303030FF"),
            FontWeight: FontWeight.Normal,
            Italic: false, Underline: false, Strikethrough: false,

            PaddingTop: 2, PaddingRight: 0, PaddingBottom: 0, PaddingLeft: 0,
            Align: Align.Left,
            LineHeight: 1.8,
            
            Fill: Color.White,
            HoverFill: ColorValue("#8dc1ed66"),
            PressedFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0),

            HoverColor: Color.Black,
            PressedColor: Color.White,     

            RadioSize: 20,
            RadioBorderColor: ColorValue("#D3D3D3FF"),
            RadioBackgroundFill: Color.White,
            RadioSelectionFill: ColorValue("#0275d8FF"),
            
            DisabledColor: RGBA(186, 186, 186, 1),
            DisabledFill: RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0),
            DisabledBorderColor: RGBA(166, 166, 166, 1)          
        }
    },

    // For the Submit Feedback dialog box.
    DialogShadow: { OffsetX: 0, OffsetY: 0, Color: "#000000", Blur: 5, Opacity: 0.5},
    DialogBox: {Fill: "#FFFFFF", Opacity: 1, BorderThickness: 0, BorderColor: "#000000", Radius: 10}
}
